This paper deals with natural language processing and representation of sentences, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also uses unsupervised learning techniques to represent sentences, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of word embeddings, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
